column5: Had tons of fun this past ice season with many family and friends. Got to bring out my two nieces to try fishing for the first time and they had a hoot from just being out there. Here is a quick video recapping my ice season. Might not be as entertaining for you, as it is for me. Great memories
great video  looks like the fishing was great too
You make great videos Kevin, 1:53 was so cool.  And the Princess rod as well.  We have some great soft water to deal with before the hard water get here again.
